lColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=12;fontColor=#232F3E;fontStyle=1;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="184" y="1074" width="900" height="20" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="rec_h_0" value="Reliability" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=11;fontColor=#DD344C;fontStyle=1;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="190" y="1104" width="296" height="18" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="rec_b_0" value="• PITR + deletion protection on Tasks table
• DLQ + redrive on SQS FIFO queue
• OnFailure DLQ for ExpireTask (async)
• OnFailure dest. on stream event source
• API Gateway throttling / usage plan" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=9.5;fontColor=#3E4C59;fontStyle=0;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="190" y="1126" width="296" height="170" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="rec_h_1" value="Security" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=11;fontColor=#8C4FFF;fontStyle=1;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="506" y="1104" width="296" height="18" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="rec_b_1" value="• Pin CORS to the Amplify origin
• Drop USER_PASSWORD_AUTH (keep SRP)
• Cognito MFA + advanced security
• SSE/KMS on SQS queue and SNS topic
• WAF on the public API; tighter IAM" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=9.5;fontColor=#3E4C59;fontStyle=0;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="506" y="1126" width="296" height="170" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="rec_h_2" value="Observability" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=11;fontColor=#1F6FB2;fontStyle=1;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="822" y="1104" width="296" height="18" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="rec_b_2" value="• CloudWatch alarms (none today)
• Enable X-Ray on API Gateway
• JSON structured logging (Globals)
• API access logs + per-method metrics
• Health dashboard for the stack" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=9.5;fontColor=#3E4C59;fontStyle=0;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="822" y="1126" width="296" height="170" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="rec_h_3" value="Cost" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=11;fontColor=#2E8B57;fontStyle=1;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1138" y="1104" width="296" height="18" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="rec_b_3" value="• Log retention (now: never expire)
• Right-size per-function memory
• Keep DynamoDB on-demand (validated)" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=9.5;fontColor=#3E4C59;fontStyle=0;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1138" y="1126" width="296" height="170" as="geometry"/></mxCell></root></mxGraphModel></diagram></mxfile>